Package: openvoicer
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Installed-Size: SIZE_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: Voicer <voicer@voicer.app>
Description: Voice-to-AI bridge for Voicer and OpenCode
 Tray application that connects Voicer (offline speech-to-text)
 with OpenCode (AI coding agent). Transcriptions are sent as
 prompts to OpenCode with popup notifications for agent status.
